Trinity::

She looked up at Archangle.  She cried out again.  Her voice echoed 
through the halls of the Cybertron Fire, "Thier dead. You won't find 
my mom and dad, they left me behind.  WWAAHHHHHH!"  (be aware, she is 
the equivalent of an 8 year old child)  She sobbed and cried. Tears 
ran down her little cheeks and started dripping off her long saber 
tooth fangs.   She whimpered and wailed. She felt scared and alone.  
Her new pred program told her to be fearless, but her spark was 
hurting from the loss of both her parents and her whole family.
